sections.History:
===[[Season 3]]===
The Ice-river clans now march in the army of [[King-Beyond-the-Wall]], [[Mance Rayder]], who has united all of the different wildling clans to assault [[the Wall]] and force their passage to the south. Mance points out that the [[Hornfoots]] hate the Ice-river clans.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Dark Wings, Dark Words]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 4]]===
Following [[Jon Snow]]'s betrayal and flight from the wildlings, he reports back to Castle Black's remaining leadership that Mance Rayder is advancing on their position with an army 100,000 strong, and that he has united the [[Thenn]]s, [[Hornfoot|Hornfoots]], and the Ice-river clans, and he even has [[Giants]] marching with him.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Two Swords]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
